* **I²C Interface:** Features an I²C interface for communication with a host microcontroller or other devices on the bus (operates at 1.8V or 3.3V)
* **VBUS Detection:** Has a built-in VBUS detection circuit to monitor the presence of a power source on the upstream port (VBUS)
* **Fault Protection:** Offers fault protection features, including over-voltage protection (OVP), under-voltage protection (UVP), and short-circuit protection (SCP)
* **Operating Temperature Range:** -40°C to +85°C (-40°F to +185°F)
